## ANU Document Delivery Service for Remote Students

The **ANU Document Delivery service** enables off-campus students to obtain materials not available in the library's digital collections. In 2025, the service processed **42,000 requests**, with **73% fulfilled within 48 hours**. This service is particularly valuable for accessing **print-only journal articles, book chapters**, and **rare materials** that haven't been digitized.

