## ANU Postal Loans: Physical Materials to Your Doorstep

The **ANU Postal Loans program** ships physical library materials directly to off-campus students' registered addresses. This service distributed **18,500 items in 2025**, with an average delivery time of **5-7 business days within Australia** and **10-14 days for international destinations**. The program covers **books, DVDs, music scores**, and other physical materials from the library's collection of **over 2.5 million print items**.

