Registration for postal loans requires **verification of current mailing address** in the student information system. International students should note that **customs regulations may affect delivery times** and availability of certain materials. The library recommends requesting items **at least 3 weeks before needed** for domestic delivery and **6 weeks for international** to ensure timely arrival. **Overdue fines are waived** for postal borrowers who experience documented shipping delays.

